					<span class="contactus_text-list-dsc">Easy and convenient.</span>

					<h3 class="contactus_text-list">● Tracks progress</h3>
					<span class="contactus_text-list-dsc">Monitors memory progress through tests every 4 months.</span>
				</div>
				<div class="m-vertical m-32 btn-wrap">
					<a class="btn is-black btn-full" href="">Buy Now</a>
				</div>
